00:42:31,000 --> 00:42:38,759
- Glory, glory Hallelujah,-
- Glory, glory Hallelujah!-

458
00:42:39,240 --> 00:42:42,710
Glory, glory Hallelujah!-

459
00:42:55,880 --> 00:42:59,634
- l wish l was in Dixie,-
- Hooray! Hooray!-

